47:42.237 --> 47:45.616
I remember one specific time
I saw Kate Schellenbach at a deli,

47:46.283 --> 47:47.367
and I didn't say hi.

47:48.410 --> 47:50.078
Maybe she didn't see me. I don't know.

47:50.162 --> 47:51.288
But if she did see me,

47:51.371 --> 47:55.167
