a very different version of me.

47:55.959 --> 47:58.629
I remember I was in the back
of the store by the coolers,

47:58.712 --> 48:00.422
and she was up front paying for something,

48:00.506 --> 48:03.008
and she was just laughing
and having fun with her friend.

48:03.842 --> 48:06.053
And I guess I didn't say hi
'cause I was embarrassed

48:06.136 --> 48:07.804
thinking about how much I'd changed.

48:10.849 --> 48:12.309
Also, speaking of change,

48:12.768 --> 48:16.605
I'd like to take a quick sidenote
to apologize to my brother, Matthew,

48:16.688 --> 48:18.565
