48:33.080 --> 48:37.584
Which brings us to Chapter 5:
"Dicks in a Box."

48:38.919 --> 48:42.965
Our record was selling like crazy,
and the shows were getting crazier.

48:43.048 --> 48:44.633
A lot of booze and a lot of cursing.

48:44.716 --> 48:48.345
Now, in the South, they were trying
to ban us for lewd behavior.

48:48.428 --> 48:51.974
We would literally have to sneak off
