so we wouldn't get arrested.

48:54.810 --> 48:56.478
The British press were around at the time,

48:56.562 --> 48:58.230
and they were writing
all these stories about us.

48:58.313 --> 49:01.316
And so by the time we got to England
to go on tour,

49:01.400 --> 49:03.277
