49:03.360 --> 49:05.654
and put them on the cover
of the actual newspapers.

49:06.613 --> 49:10.242
So there was this weird expectation
for us to be fucking maniacs.

49:11.326 --> 49:15.831
We really did not do that. Just as
a sidenote, that just did not happen.

49:22.296 --> 49:26.466
Seriously, I do like it though.
