49:26.550 --> 49:28.135
-I really like that. But--
-Yeah.

49:28.218 --> 49:31.054
You know, it's too bad that didn't stick.

49:31.138 --> 49:32.806
-"Horrible" Horovitz?
-Yeah, it's a good name.

49:32.890 --> 49:35.309
There was an actual meeting of Parliament

49:35.392 --> 49:38.145
to decide whether they should let us
into the UK or not.

49:38.604 --> 49:39.855
Seriously.

49:39.938 --> 49:44.151
With each city we went to on the tour,
the crowd developed a

49:44.234 --> 49:45.986
"you motherfuckers ain't shit

49:46.069 --> 49:48.655
compared to us here" type of vibe, right?

49:49.364 --> 49:53.368
So by the time we got to
the last show of that tour in Liverpool,

49:53.452 --> 49:55.329
the punters went berserk.

49:56.163 --> 49:59.499
Right into the first song
of our show in Liverpool,

49:59.583 --> 50:02.961
