53:17.406 --> 53:18.949
Do you wanna help me wash this car?

53:20.075 --> 53:21.076
Now?

53:33.881 --> 53:34.882
Okay.

53:36.758 --> 53:37.885
Okay, so...

53:38.927 --> 53:41.638
That was a movie I was in
right after the Licensed to Ill tour.

53:42.431 --> 53:45.184
It's called Lost Angels, and it's awful.

53:45.267 --> 53:47.102
Please don't go look it up, okay?

53:47.186 --> 53:49.021
Please don't look it up and watch it.

53:49.646 --> 53:50.689
Please don't.

53:50.772 --> 53:51.773
Anyways...

53:53.233 --> 53:54.776
The last 12 months of touring

53:54.860 --> 53:57.946
felt like a tornado had ripped me
